image_analysis.description: A photograph of a luxurious bathroom interior. The foreground shows a marble countertop with a white undermount sink and a gold-toned faucet. To the left, there is a large mirror with ornate gold framing and decorative oval wall sconces. A small lamp with a white shade is mounted on the wall. In the background, an open wooden door leads to a smaller room containing a toilet and a framed black-and-white artwork of a zebra. To the right, a portion of a patterned chair or ottoman is visible. A white piece of paper with the letter 'M' is taped to the wall near the doorway.
image_analysis.layout: Interior architectural photograph with a view through an open doorway.
